description: Set atop The Mezz, this top-floor corner home delivers light, privacy, and sweeping views of downtown Boston and Thomas Park. The two-bedroom, one-bath layout is framed by oversized windows and tall ceilings, creating an airy retreat above the city. The open kitchen and living space features Bosch appliances, quartz countertops, and a generous island designed for entertaining, dining, or working from home. A private balcony extends the living area outdoors, perfect for morning coffee or evening sunsets. Two deeded garage parking spaces, elevator access, and a shared roof terrace with club room add convenience and lifestyle flexibility. Located in a boutique building, you’ll enjoy quiet comfort without sacrificing proximity to Broadway’s growing dining scene, public transit, Seaport, Logan Airport, and downtown. This move-in-ready condo blends design, amenities, and location in one of South Boston’s most connected and walkable neighborhoods.
